      <title>南非大选：灯光能否继续照耀？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-27/south-africa-election-can-the-lights-stay-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非在选举前夕正享受着罕见的不间断电力供应，对于这个已经习惯了持续多年的每日停电的国家来说，更多的是怀疑而不是赞扬。彭博社记者 Jennifer Zabasajja 报道。  （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-27/south-africa-election-can-the-lights-stay-on</guid>
